dmca.title: Notification of Copyright Infringement at www.photoradarspray.com

To Whom It May Concern:

The URL in question is currently not accessible as of 11:06:22 a.m. (GMT-6)
on January 16, 2006.

Legal Response Team
The Planet

-----Original Message-----
From: ON TRACK Manufacturing Corp. [mailto:info@ontrackcorp.com]

To: copyright@theplanet.com
Subject: Notification of Copyright Infringement at www.photoradarspray.com
Importance: High

Attn: Mr. George Poletes, Corporate Counsel Servermatrix.com aka
ThePlanet.com Internet Services, Inc.
1333 Stemmons Freeway, Suite 110
Dallas, TX 75207
Tel: 214-782-7800

Dear George,

Please find attached in PDF file notice of copyright infringement on the
website http://www.photoradarspray.com/ hosted by your company.

This information has also been faxed to you at: 214-782-7756.
Our fax indicates that all 18 pages have been received successfully.

Please confirm receipt of this information by phone, fax or email.

Thank you.

Regards,

Mrs. D. Michelle Pasek
